commit.message:
Implement full auth routing and session guards across all pages

supabase.ts: explicit persistSession/autoRefreshToken/detectSessionInUrl config

AuthLoader: new full-screen logo-pulse loader shown during session checks

Landing page (/): convert to client component; check session on mount;
redirect logged-in users to /app via router.replace before any render;
show AuthLoader while checking; unauthenticated users see landing normally

Login page (/login): show AuthLoader while checking existing session;
read ?redirect=<path> query param; after signin use router.replace(redirectTo)
instead of router.push('/app'); Google OAuth redirectTo respects redirect param;
already-logged-in users redirected to redirectTo immediately

Signup page (/signup): show AuthLoader while checking session; redirect
already-logged-in users to /app; after OTP verified use router.replace('/app')
instead of router.push; fix stale 8-box OTP reset to 6 boxes

Dashboard (/app): auth guard now passes ?redirect=%2Fapp to /login;
onAuthStateChange distinguishes SIGNED_OUT (→ /) from token expiry
(→ /login?redirect=%2Fapp) for correct cross-tab signout behaviour;
handleSignOut uses router.replace('/') instead of router.push('/')

WaitlistCTA: "Get Started Free" now routes to /signup instead of fake form

